  "content": [
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Backgroud：GEELY  has OS ErrorHook issue Occasionally, only once."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "After Analysis："
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Wed Jun 14 08:52:14 2023"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "0D0204010730390001"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Wed Jun 14 08:52:14 2023"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "0D020401073039000C0107E5070701F3 -> 0x39 -> Vector OS ErrorHook error OSServiceId_SetRelAlarm , E_OS_STATE"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/Improve%20OS%20ErrorHook%20log/image-2023-7-28_13-0-26.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/Improve OS ErrorHook log/image-2023-7-28_13-0-26.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Most likely one of the three below："
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "SetRelAlarm(evtCfg->eventList[evID].osAlarm, waitTime, 0);"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "SetRelAlarm(EventPropertiesPtr->eventConfig[evID].osAlarm,EventPropertiesPtr→eventConfig[evID].osWaitingTime_ms,0);"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "SetRelAlarm(ALR_SystemM_CommonSequencer, SYSTEMMNGR_CYCLE_TIME, 0);"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "But have no more information to Identify which one is."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "So add more information in ErrorHook(), to print which Task, ISR, and Alarm if  OSServiceId_SetRelAlarm."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "RTC:"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "https://rb-alm-20-p.de.bosch.com/ccm/web/projects/ECARX#action=com.ibm.team.workitem.viewWorkItem&id=1808774"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Reference（SetRelAlarm issue in GW VCU）:"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "GM-VCU shutdown pullback issue:"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "FW Shutdown pullback during NvM_WriteAll.msg"
    }
  ],
